Text: I think you spelled it wrong, its The Invisible Douche. My gf uses it, for a springtime fresh Ceutsch ... err cooch.

I love, love the springtime fresh cooch. Just yummy. May I suggest a delectable yogurt dressing, with liberal amounts of chopped fresh basil and a bit of parsely, sage, rosemary and thyme mixed in? Belissimo. Muah! She'll love it too! Hand on heart.
yeah but that wouldnt be invisible, it would just be another bukkake flick
